Title: Can faulty modules be predicted by warning messages of static code analyzer?
UseOF-SZZ: The source code module is obtained from this project by the SZZ
Summary: They try to introduce a new metric as a fault-prone predictor. The metric is 'frequency of particular words'
Outcome: (1) can fault-prone modules be predicted by applying a text filter to the warning messages of static code analyzer?--> YES
